frames.caption: An elderly man with a white beard is rowing a small boat through rough seas. He wears a straw hat and a weathered shirt, appearing focused and determined amidst the crashing waves.
frames.description: The scene depicts an elderly man navigating a small boat through turbulent ocean waters. The sky is overcast, suggesting an impending storm, and the man is engaged in rowing, showcasing resilience and determination.

frames.caption: An elderly man with a white beard is seated in a small boat, gripping a fishing rod. He wears a straw hat and a weathered shirt, surrounded by choppy ocean waves under a cloudy sky.
